item.title: This Quiz Will Reveal If You Can Spell 'Leash' - See If You Pass!
item.description: Introduction Do you think you can spell the word “leash”? Have you ever been asked to spell it and weren’t sure if you got it right? Well, this quiz is here to help you find out! Definition of “Leash” A leash is a strap or cord that is used to restrain an animal, usually a dog. It is usually made of leather, nylon, or other strong material. Purpose of Quiz The purpose of this quiz is to test your spelling ability when it comes to the word “leash”.
